{"tid":2089354,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]我諗到新嘅抗爭方法 唔知幫唔幫到手 希望大家俾啲意見","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T16:13:38.000Z","uid":181549,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5d224ed0428884cc70158e7e3dd11f86314d602b","tid":2089354,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"早前我出左個post，都多人討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>黨安法過左 應承我減少所有無謂消費<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2085821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2085821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我諗到啲新野<br />\n人係會有物慾<br />\n一時三刻好難要大家戒曬啲無謂消費<br />\n我諗緊如果大家真係要買野 買哂黃色得唔得<br />\n大家屌我痴撚線都得 討論下 唔OK就當參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UEvcgHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUEvcgHk.jpg&h=8f05e546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJOdLAF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJOdLAF.jpg&h=c0a64d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返工/坐車用嘅卡套<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4MSgHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4MSgHm.jpg&h=33b20978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoDYcfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoDYcfH.jpg&h=d19aa35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出去行山跑步沙灘用毛巾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPXmUt2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPXmUt2.jpg&h=2189da58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買野用嘅環保袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUzwxfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUzwxfJ.jpg&h=dff9ec3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼身衣物要換可以揀下黃色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFDJonp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFDJonp.jpg&h=158fc24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XE3xgHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXE3xgHp.jpg&h=3c393b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶飯用嘅飯盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTSRxfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTSRxfM.jpg&h=a8ce24c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃色餐具 食飯都開心啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/01/231933_a79fa68321328869714ae6f03600340c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F01%2F231933_a79fa68321328869714ae6f03600340c.jpeg&h=89868980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個可能係無謂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果真係要買 揀黃色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reMfeuA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreMfeuA.jpg&h=3303cbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任何黃色吊飾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6p793nV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6p793nV.jpg&h=0be4f400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人有壓力 打下機獎勵下自己都要揀黃色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTS93nW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTS93nW.jpg&h=b8d64917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之乜撚都黃色<br />\n最好揀埋非中国產貨"},{"pid":"4df1ca1b6c0c72877e8a81f10588c4d1b08d5bff","tid":2089354,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967b809bb160e0b94b9cd6a2435e2ba21a2ea547","tid":2089354,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4df1ca1b6c0c72877e8a81f10588c4d1b08d5bff","tid":2089354,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"俾啲意見啦..話我痴線都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293607a79064a1e7ff214f22fc9c66baf26adc92","tid":2089354,"uid":100904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"比卡超啊，亞古獸啊"},{"pid":"3233ee912a8ba1b27c6ce18911d2d6f4c9cb33cc","tid":2089354,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2lehohm/5r790002q45812qs4231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2lehohm%2F5r790002q45812qs4231.jpg&h=5464064b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5d43dd2a8108b89ed318f1696d42da1602d92f3","tid":2089354,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"293607a79064a1e7ff214f22fc9c66baf26adc92","tid":2089354,"uid":100904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"比卡超啊，亞古獸啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"最緊要黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6422d88ebb68ba2c9ce9c8c9349803e59a4ea076","tid